### Version
3.1.1

### Environment
window7、chrome、react-router4

### Reproduction link
[https://github.com/lixuguang88/blog/tree/master/react/antd/table](https://github.com/lixuguang88/blog/tree/master/react/antd/table)

### Steps to reproduce
1. 注册Table pagination的onChange事件， 更改页面search的值，同是更新 pagination.current 值，
2. componentDidUpdate 里面比对两次search的值，更新 pagination.current 值，


*  用浏览器的前进，后退，偶尔出现多个激活button，点击页面才能消失
* table loading =true 的时候出现滚动条 . [更改样式](https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/blob/master/components/spin/style/index.less#L26) 添加left：0;

主要代码 ：
```js

  componentDidUpdate(prevPrpos){
    const search = this.props.location.search;
    if(search !== prevPrpos.location.search){
      //不同page
      let page =  search  ?  parseInt(search.slice(6), 10) : 1;
      this.setState({
        current: page
      })
      this.fetchData(page)
    }
  }

  pagerChange(current){
    const { history, match} = this.props;
    if(current){
      history.push({
        pathname: match.url,
        search: `?page=${current}`
      })
    }
    this.setState({
      current: current
    })
  }

  render(){
    let match = this.props.match;
    let columnRender = columns(match.url);

    return (
      <div style={{width: 1200, margin: '50px auto'}}>
        <Table bordered pagination={{
          current: this.state.current,
          total: 100,
          onChange: e => this.pagerChange(e)
        }} loading={this.state.ajax} 
        columns={columnRender} 
        dataSource={this.state.data}
        rowKey={record => record.id}
      />
     </div>
    )
  }
```

### What is expected?
不要出现多个激活按钮
没有滚动条


